title: 'MythBusters' Closes with Final Season in 2016
text: 'MythBusters' Closes with Final Season in 2016 Saturday, 24 October 2015 (15 minutes ago) Fans of the science entertainment television program " MythBusters " will have to say goodbye to the show soon as reports say that it's going to air its final season. According to a report by My News LA, the show will end with season 14 next year.
